---
<section class="action" id="action">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>BECOME A<br>FOUNDING<br>MEMBER</h2>
    <p class="lead">
      You don't need to be a developer or a lawyer.
      You just need to show up.
    </p>
    <div class="action-grid">
      <div class="action-card">
        <span class="icon">💚</span>
        <h3>Donate</h3>
        <p>Every dollar signals to funders that this community is organized. Pledges are non-binding and collected only when we're ready to act.</p>
        <a href="/calculator" class="btn-sm">Pledge Now</a>
      </div>
      <div class="action-card">
        <span class="icon">✍️</span>
        <h3>Sign the Petition</h3>
        <p>Every signature shows the city and our grant partners that Montavilla wants a voice in what happens at 7700 SE Stark.</p>
        <a href="/#petition" class="btn-sm">Sign Now</a>
      </div>
      <div class="action-card">
        <span class="icon">📢</span>
        <h3>Spread the Word</h3>
        <p>Print our flyer. Post on social. Tell every neighbor. This campaign wins through grassroots reach — one conversation at a time.</p>
        <a href="/#petition" class="btn-sm">Get Materials</a>
      </div>
      <div class="action-card">
        <span class="icon">🤝</span>
        <h3>Join the Steering Committee</h3>
        <p>Bring skills in law, finance, design, organizing, or communications to the core team building this land trust.</p>
        <a href="/#petition" class="btn-sm">Get Involved</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

